x-sap-shortText: API to manage the information about employee absences

info.title: Time Off
info.description:
You can use these APIs to manage employee absences including vacation, sick leave, and other paid time off.

 You can find your company's API server in [List of API Servers in SAP SuccessFactors.](https://help.sap.com/viewer/d599f15995d348a1b45ba5603e2aba9b/LATEST/en-US/af2b8d5437494b12be88fe374eba75b6.html)

externalDocs.description: More Information about Time Off APIs available in help.sap.com
